# ExtractorAOIs Service - API Refactoring Guide

## Overview

This guide shows how to refactor the ExtractorAOIs Windows Service to use REST APIs instead of direct SQL queries.

**Status**: ✅ All API endpoints are ready and tested (0 compilation errors)

---

## Available API Endpoints

### AOI Machine Management

| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `/AOI/GetMachineConfig?aoiId={id}` | GET | Get specific machine config |
| `/AOI/GetMachinesByStation?stationId={id}` | GET | Get all machines for a station |
| `/AOI/GetAllActiveMachines` | GET | Get all active machines |

### AOI Inspection Data

| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `/AOI/SubmitInspection` | POST | Submit single inspection record |
| `/AOI/SubmitInspectionBatch` | POST | Submit multiple records |

### AOI Program Counter Management

| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `/AOI/GetProgramCounter?aoiId={id}&partId={id}&side={T/B}` | GET | Get program counter |
| `/AOI/UpdateProgramCounter?aoiId={id}&partId={id}&side={T/B}&counter={value}` | POST | Update counter |
| `/AOI/CreateOrUpdateProgram?aoiId={id}&partId={id}&side={T/B}&arrQty={qty}&counter={value}` | POST | Upsert program |

