### Example 4: Batch Insert (Performance Optimization)

#### ✅ NEW CAPABILITY (Batch API)

```vb
' Build list of inspection records
Dim requests As New List(Of AOIInspectionRequest)

For Each rowSSN As DataRow In dtBoardBarcodes.Rows
    Dim request As New AOIInspectionRequest With {
        .Sn = rowSSN("Barcode"),
        .Aoiid = AOIID,
        .StationId = StationID,
        .PartId = partid,
        .Side = sideid,
        .Trndate = Fecha,
        .IsGood = (rowSSN("Result") = "PASS"),
        .Position = rowSSN("Position"),
        .FacilityKey = 1,
        .AreaId = AreaID
    }
    requests.Add(request)
Next

' Submit all at once (much faster than individual inserts)
Dim batchResponse As AOIBatchResponse = AOI.SubmitInspectionBatch(requests)

WriteToFile($"Batch Result: {batchResponse.SuccessfulRecords}/{batchResponse.TotalRecords} successful")

If batchResponse.FailedRecords > 0 Then
    For Each errorMsg In batchResponse.Errors
        WriteToFile("Batch Error: " & errorMsg)
    Next
End If
```

**Benefits:**
- ✅ **10-100x faster** than individual inserts
- ✅ Single API call for multiple records
- ✅ Detailed error reporting per batch
- ✅ Transactional integrity

